      <title>当旋风前往布里斯班时，澳大利亚的东海岸警觉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/australia-s-east-coast-on-alert-as-cyclone-on-track-for-brisbane</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的东海岸正在为异常高的潮汐冲浪，强烈的降雨，破坏性风和威胁生命的洪水做好准备，因为预计旋风将在本周晚些时候在该国第三大城市附近登陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/australia-s-east-coast-on-alert-as-cyclone-on-track-for-brisbane</guid>
